text:
ClickUp is incredible. Have you heard of Layla Pomper of <http://ProcessDriven.co|ProcessDriven.co>? She puts out YouTube Clickup Content and it's incredible. So much so I joined her ClickingUp community.

That said, I use ClickUp for Google My Business posts with my copy writer.

I write the direction on the post in the comments area. Use custom field with statuses. I do 4or 5 at a time in a month. Change the status to with copywriter. Then she puts the copy inside the task description. Then changes the custom field status to in review. I share with clients. Upon approval, I change all of them to 'ready to publish'. Then they get sent over to a Google Sheet with Integromat.

If that sounds helpful to know... I can send a Loom with more details and visuals.
